queries.query:
from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "MCP_HighVoltVS_Voltage")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "output_value")

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "ThrottleADC")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "output_value")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "RightTurnOn" or r["_measurement"] == "PowerSaveOn" or r["_measurement"] == "ReverseOn" or r["_measurement"] == "RearviewOn" or r["_measurement"] == "LeftTurnOn" or r["_measurement"] == "LockOn" or r["_measurement"] == "CruiseUpOn" or r["_measurement"] == "HornOn" or r["_measurement"] == "CruiseDownOn")
  |> tail(n: 1)
  |> group()

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Thermistor_MaxTemp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "output_value")

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "RegenADC")

  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_1" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_0" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_10" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_11" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_12" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_13" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_14" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_15" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_16" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_17" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_18" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_19" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_2" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_20" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_21" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_22" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_23" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_24" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_25" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_26" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_27" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_28" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_29" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_3" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_30" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_4" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_5" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_6" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_7" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_8" or r["_measurement"] == "CellVoltages_9")
  |> tail(n : 1)
  |> group()

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "output_value")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)

states = [
    "STARTUP",
    "LV_SWITCH_ENABLE",
    "PRECHARGE_ENABLE",
    "LOWSIDE_SHUT",
    "HIGHSIDE_SHUT",
    "LV_BUCK_ENABLE",
    "PACK_NORMAL",
    "FAULTED",
    "HIGHSIDE_OPEN",
    "LOWSIDE_OPEN",
    "PRECHARGE_DISABLE"
]

from(bucket: "Telemetry")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "BMS_State")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: states[ int(v: r._value) ] }))
